Be careful about adding extra traces into an unrelated commit.

be careful about extra lines
Removed the extra line.

Is this needed?
Even if so, I think two BMCWEB_LOG_DEBUG entries can be combined into one entry.

I had to add service and path debug as those are ifdefed. I kept on separate BMCWEB_LOG_DEBUG because it prints long string so wanted to keep them separate as compared to before. Other option is to use "__attribute__((unused))" for service and path.

Then, yes, it may be better to use 
```
[[maybe_unused]]const std::string& service, [[maybe_unused]]const std::string& path,
```
